author: Warhammer
description:
As the Chapter Master of the Raven Guard, Aethon Shaan is one of the most deadly and stealthy of the brothers he commands. Emma is going to show you how to paint him in this video, which can also be used as a guide for painting the rest of your Raven Guard army!

Here’s a list of the paints we used in today’s video:

Base:
Abaddon Black
Corax White
Iron Hands Steel
Khorne Red
Rakarth Flesh
Rhinox Hide
Runelord Brass

Layer:
Eshin Grey
Pallid Wych Flesh
Stormhost Silver
White Scar

Contrast:
Frostheart
Ratling Grime

Shade:
Soulblight Grey

Technical:
Lahmian Medium 

Tools:
L Base
S Layer
M Layer
S Dry
